      <a href="summary.html" class="btn-cute py-2 px-4 rounded text-sm bg-pink-200">üìä ‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="cute-card p-6 rounded-xl shadow mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">üìí ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ß‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£</h2>
      <ul id="transaction-list" class="space-y-2 max-h-60 overflow-y-auto"></ul>
    </div>

    <div class="cute-card p-6 rounded-xl shadow">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">üéÄ ‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏ü‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏à‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢</h2>
      <canvas id="expense-chart" height="100"></canvas>
    </div>
